snippet.title: HANG OUT WITH US | food, skin, makeup | iluvsarahii
snippet.description:
A day in my life kinda vibessss❤️
Im very excited to hang out with you guys and show you how I make my spicy avocado toast , do my makeup and talk skincare.
And I also want to thank L’Oreal for partnering with me in today’s video to talk to you guys about the 30 day challenge that I just completed with them.  Back in November I joined the challenge where I would be trading in my luxury Retinol for their Revitalift Pure Retinol and OMGGG, this product is fire!! It’s so effective and powerful yet so hydrating and soothing so i I love the brightness and radiance it left on my skin!!! 

If you’re Interested in trying the Puré Retinol click here to shop 🛍 

https://bit.ly/3p8R786

KVD Brow Pomade in Medium brown 
Artist Couture X Static Jon Club Daddy Palette 
Lancôme Idole Mascara

snippet.title: CARNE ASADA CUP OF NOODLES | iluvsarahii
snippet.description:
What are we getting into today? 🤤🔥
Sit back, relax and enjoy this Carne asada cup of noddles. I know this looks crazy but trust me it’s sooooooo delicious!!!! Enjoy xo 

Thanks to the OG creator for the recipe! Watch his video too! https://youtu.be/Zq0h-VcYVyY

Vegetable Chopper Mandoline Slicer https://www.amazon.com/dp/B07JGXJCQY/ref=cm_sw_r_cp_api_i_luLLEbZ7ADTPM

FOLLOW US 
@iluvsarahii @ayysebas 

Ingredients for 2👫
Cup of noddles 
Carne asada 
1 Onion 
3 Bell peppers
1-2 Tomato 
Cilantro 
Cabbage 
Jalapeño 
Salt and pepper 
Oil 
Spicy mayo (mayonnaise and Sriracha) 
Soy sauce 





This video is not sponsored

I usually move a lot of things around too so if you decorating and it doesn’t look right just move it around, it will find its home :)

snippet.title: SPICY CUCUMBER MARGARITA | iluvsarahii
snippet.description:
Bienvenidos amigos🥒🔥 In today’s video we are  going to be teaching you how to make this delicious Spicy Cucumber Margarita! 
This drink is so refreshing , so tasty and perfect for the warmer days approaching or whenever you’re thirsty. 




Use my Discount code: ILUVSARAHII on 
cheilitaschamoy.com  or @CheilitasChamoy

(The Discount code provided is an affiliation code with Cheilitas Chamoy, i do receive a small percentage from sales) 


Ingredients 
Per drink 
Half a Cucumber (cut in half then cut into slices ) 
Serranos 
2oz or 2 Shots Reposado tequila
2oz fresh lime juice 
1 oz Agave 
Ice
Cheilitas Chamoy
Tajín

Also maker sure to have a shaker, don’t muddle , don’t blend , SHAKE IT ALL!  Enjoy! Xo

snippet.description:
Hiiii everyone, So today’s video is all about my decision on getting new veneers. For those who don’t know i recently re-did my veneers so I wanted to open up about why i decided to redo , why i got them in the first place and also share with you guys my entire journey with my teeth from before veneers to now. Xo
